{"tid":426823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳歐陽桂芬：陳馮富珍當選世衛總幹事是上帝抬舉中國人","createTime":"2017-10-07T03:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T09:59:24.000Z","uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb4ffc1154845fcdbf4bdd5ee1e15e9d72cb633","tid":426823,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"今天是中華人民共和國成立68周年，祝福香港復興團隊舉行「十月一香港祈禱日」，儼如國慶活動。以勒基金總幹事陳歐陽桂芬在早場祈禱環節時，提及陳馮富珍11年前當選世衛總幹事之事，形容「是上帝抬舉中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n陳歐陽桂芬表示，世衛11年前要選出新一屆總幹事，大部份會員國都共識要選一個亞洲人，因為經歷沙士疫情後，大家都相信下一次沙士會再在亞洲爆發，最後由中國支持的陳馮富珍當選。陳歐陽桂芬忽然說：「上帝後來點樣講法？佢話陳馮富珍一定可以坐到呢個位，不過唔係因為佢係亞洲人，唔係因為佢做過醫生，唔係因為佢處理過病毒，而係因為上帝要抬舉中國人！」<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，11年後的今天，上帝抬舉整個中國富強起來，是藉著香港人祝福中國人。「邊個叫中國人做『強國人』係我哋香港人叫佢哋做『強國人』，叫咗幾年，佢由唔強都變咗強！」陳歐陽桂芬身後的詩班人員都忍不住笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apostlesmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/03-1068x599.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F03-1068x599.jpg&h=f600f2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連上帝都要比面支那<br />\n支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945aaab459d3d9ce8b8ab396e9bf310199b85f12","tid":426823,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"傻撚左個鼻？"},{"pid":"da5fec8859bb44973236a4299a79c785a0c3baea","tid":426823,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19d7cf1eef7a004842462cde1b988027d7810a5","tid":426823,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"有冇片？"},{"pid":"164a904ad92d3d5ced76ee56af833c294d7b6e37","tid":426823,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"雞真自小接受英國文化<br />\n講英語 寫英文 慶祝聖誕<br />\n依支那人邏輯應該係英國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd6479aa393d5cecd99e973eb71532495f6aff5","tid":426823,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞真自小接受英國文化<br />\n講英語 寫英文 慶祝聖誕<br />\n依支那人邏輯應該係英國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係冠夫姓呢樣嘢<br />\n支那人已經淘汰咗"},{"pid":"40f7b5de146ae7127e9b1e9f538038d54baf5ef3","tid":426823,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"中國人係炎黃子孫<br />\n幾時變做上帝耶和華兒女！？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daed38d3b4e748b0baec2389fdacca463f26324","tid":426823,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人係炎黃子孫<br />\n幾時變做上帝耶和華兒女！？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n共匪：上帝係中國人"},{"pid":"2547e920bfa628b76598471fa251d714280809a5","tid":426823,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國人係炎黃子孫<br />\n幾時變做上帝耶和華兒女！？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n共匪：上帝係中國人</blockquote><br />\n冇錯 挪亞方舟 舟八口"},{"pid":"85ecf62f19402df493b3c1654a09c123ff0f99c8","tid":426823,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"上帝經常比人老屈"},{"pid":"4fe7acee0620ced8161b08950bd67ecb60f1849b","tid":426823,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"已經係複姓<br />\n仲要走去冠夫姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d33f0bd7988eccb0335f24fbbba41737383fa56","tid":426823,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"c1caf4b9968803a9e1ee3cfbbedb7aae4c8a40ba","tid":426823,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「邊個叫中國人做『強國人』係我哋香港人叫佢哋做『強國人』，叫咗幾年，佢由唔強都變咗強！」陳歐陽桂芬身後的詩班人員都忍不住笑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/03/10/1687_20160310161600_56e12d40c3081.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F03%2F10%2F1687_20160310161600_56e12d40c3081.gif&h=9a40cb33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd23d21a424c75c23ccb36f963e29ffa23a2ddba","tid":426823,"uid":79138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"雞珍心諗我本事坐上去 又要關中國人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aab548d56fc71824e0538da97eb734d3e4ff401","tid":426823,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞珍心諗我本事坐上去 又要關中國人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n共享呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家陣興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02171bcd3fe6dfa1858f6d23e6ddb62579b3f90c","tid":426823,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">什麼人算是「上帝的百姓」？我們可能馬上回答：「以色列人！」沒錯，在創世記十二章，上帝的確揀選亞伯拉罕，叫他成為大國，他的後裔必作上帝的子民。</span>「耶和華的使者」在出埃及記三章「從荊棘裡火焰中向摩西顯現」；摩西觀看焚而不火毀的大異象，同時認識了全知全能的上帝，上帝從荊棘裡對摩西說：「我是你父親的　神，是亞伯拉罕的　神、以撒的　神、雅各的　神......我的百姓在埃及所受的困苦，我實在看見了；他們因受督工的轄制所發的哀聲，我也聽見了。<br />\n<br />\n上帝耶和華揀選子民係以色列人<br />\n幾時變成中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911b332608163d73ae4b13fde71613b4bd7a92e0","tid":426823,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:48:13.000Z","msg":"抬舉個字義唔係通常都包括住譽過其實嘅意思咩<br />\n<br />\n抬舉係佢原話？<br />\n如果係&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c5b5067d04794df7aaf866ae4167969df7290b","tid":426823,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抬舉個字義唔係通常都包括住譽過其實嘅意思咩<br />\n<br />\n抬舉係佢原話？<br />\n如果係&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國人「被提」了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaee06c0940de8012f0837939671e859d3f797e","tid":426823,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"如果個老公姓司徒咪司徒歐陽桂芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30418e554cb19485712ac4586d9c0fc15d3eb597","tid":426823,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."}]}